    {
      "name": "add_issue",
      "description": "Create a new support issue/ticket in the ERPClaw system. Use this when a customer reports a bug, feature request, complaint, or other support need. Required: --subject. For priority use 'low', 'medium', 'high', 'critical'. For issue-type use 'bug', 'feature_request', 'question', 'complaint', 'return'. Related: update-issue for status changes, list-issues to see all tickets.",
